<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erreur</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ website_description() }}">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}

    {% block javascripts %}
        {{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main-wrap">
        {% include 'includes/_header.html.twig' %}
        
        <main>
            <section class="rounded-3 alert alert-danger p-2 text-center mt-5">
                <h2 class="h4">Il y a eu une erreur</h2>
                <p class="mt-3">Le site a rencontré une erreur. Veuillez vous rapprocher de l'administrateur.</p>
                <p>Retour à l'<a href="/">accueil</a>.</p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>